# ⚙️ Installation

Clone the repository

```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/estatehub-api.git

cd estatehub-api
```

Install dependencies

```bash
npm install
```

Create a `.env` file

```env
PORT=5000

MONGODB_URI=

JWT_SECRET=

CLIENT_URL=http://localhost:3000

CLOUDINARY_CLOUD_NAME=

CLOUDINARY_API_KEY=

CLOUDINARY_API_SECRET=

EMAIL_USER=

EMAIL_PASS=

OPENAI_API_KEY=

STRIPE_SECRET_KEY=

STRIPE_WEBHOOK_SECRET=
```

Run development server

```bash
npm run dev
```

Build project

```bash
npm run build
```

Run production

```bash
npm start
```

---

# 📡 API Endpoints

## Authentication

```
POST   /user/register
POST   /user/login
GET    /user/profile
PATCH  /user/profile
```

---

## Properties

```
POST    /property
GET     /property
GET     /property/:id
PATCH   /property/:id
DELETE  /property/:id
```

---

## Categories

```
GET     /category
POST    /category
PATCH   /category/:id
DELETE  /category/:id
```

---

## Bookings

```
POST    /booking
GET     /booking
PATCH   /booking/:id
DELETE  /booking/:id
```

---

## Reviews

```
POST   /review
GET    /review/property/:propertyId
PATCH  /review/:id
DELETE /review/:id
```

---

## Messages

```
POST   /message
GET    /message/:userId
GET    /message/unread/count
PATCH  /message/:id/read
```

---

## Notifications

```
GET    /notification
GET    /notification/unread
PATCH  /notification/:id/read
PATCH  /notification/read-all
```

---

## Payments

```
POST   /payment/booking/:bookingId
POST   /payment/subscription
POST   /payment/webhook
GET    /payment/history
GET    /payment/:id
```

---

## Subscriptions

```
GET    /subscription/plans
POST   /subscription
GET    /subscription/me
PATCH  /subscription/cancel
```

---

## Admin

```
GET    /admin/dashboard
GET    /analytics/admin
```

---

## Agent

```
GET    /agent/dashboard
```

---

# 🔌 Socket.IO Events

## Client → Server

```
join
typing
stopTyping
messageRead
```

## Server → Client

```
newMessage
newNotification
typing
stopTyping
messageRead
```

---

# 🔒 Roles

| Role     | Permissions                                    |
| -------- | ---------------------------------------------- |
| Admin    | Full System Access                             |
| Agent    | Manage Properties, Bookings, Messages          |
| Customer | Browse Properties, Bookings, Reviews, Payments |

